    "A GAN with noisy data added for DTI prediction is depicted in Fig. 7.",
    "In 2022, attention was focused on the reinforcing effects of attentional perception and transfer learning on GAI in drug discovery.",
    "51 proposed the HGAN method, which constructs a heterogeneous graph attention network with an added graph attention diffusion layer.",
    "This method captures more indirect node information from both intra-and inter-layer perspectives, enlarging the receptive field and enhancing attention perception.",
    "The study also found that varying the degree of receptive field expansion within and between layers leads to different effects."
